reviewText: I haven't had time to watch all disc, but the ones i have watched are great.
I enjoyed it. The best one is Lisa Ann.

Beautiful women, however; every short scene is the same. VERY top-heavy with oral sex, and the rest of the scene shot from across the room, with soft jazzy music.  Absolutely predictable (did I say every scene was the same?) and over-produced..  Turns these ultra hot women into boring mind numbing nothings...  I wouldnt buy this again, or anything produced by this studio.  They have no imagination at all.....
